Mail Manager is offered to you under the concepts of ShareWare.

You can use it for an evaluation period of up to 4 weeks without paying any charge. If you are going to use Mail Manager after the evaluation period, you MUST register.

To ease your moral decision, the unregistered version of Mail Manager also has some limitations:

